Package: NOAA
Type: Package
Title: Read, Cleanse and Visualise NOAA Dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wing THAM
Maintainer: Wing THAM <wingtham@abc.com>
Description: The package implements methods to cleanse the NOAA dataset. NOAA stands for U.S. National Oceanographic and Atmospheric Administration, 
    the dataset contain significant earthquakes around the world. The aim of the package is to cleanse the dataset so that it can be visualised in
    two ways: Timeline by plotting the selected earthquakes, and interactive map showing the latitude and longitude with relevant information as
    pop up of the earthquakes.
